gomodel:SYNGO_2428  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Quantitative proteomic analysis of synaptosomes prepared from rat brains showes that on average presynaptic terminals have ~ 4000 copies of the VAMP1 protein. Experimental description: Materials & Methods:\nSynaptosomes were purified from adult Wistar rats (five to six weeks old) as\npreviously described (35, 6)." ;
